Welcome to Tagxedo, word cloud with styles

   Tagxedo turns words -- famous speeches, news articles, slogans and
   themes, even your love letters -- into a visually stunning word cloud,
   words individually sized appropriately to highlight the frequencies of
   occurrence within the body of text.

   Start Now, or make a Tagxedo out of your blogs, tweets, or tags...
