   Please install Silverlight. If you have already installed Silverlight
   and Tagxedo still does not work, please try it on a different browser.
   In particular, Google Chrome no longer supports Silverlight. Firefox,
   Safari, and even Internet Explorer each has its own peculiarity with
   respect to Silverlight, some in the form of version-specific bug.
   Finally, Tagxedo only works on Desktop or Laptop computers...

